import React from 'react'
import { Container } from '../../GlobalStyles'
import { SignInForm, Title, Input, SignUpLink, ConnectButton, InputWrapper } from './SignIn.elements'
import {FaUserAlt} from 'react-icons/fa'
import {BsUnlockFill} from 'react-icons/bs'

const SignIn = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Container>
      <SignInForm>
        <Title>Se connecter</Title>
        <InputWrapper>
            <FaUserAlt/>
            <Input placeholder='Email' type='email'/>
        </InputWrapper>
        <InputWrapper>
            <BsUnlockFill/>
            <Input placeholder='Mot de passe' type='passeword'/>
        </InputWrapper>
        <SignUpLink>Vous n'etes pas encore menmbre ? Rejoignez-nous</SignUpLink>
        <ConnectButton>Se connecter</ConnectButton>
      </SignInForm>
    </Container>
    </>
  )
}

export default SignIn
